1. The upload/installation of the plugin can be done using admin interface, or manually unpack it to campsite/implementation/site/plugins folder.

2. Enable the plugin, and set sufficient admin rights via the stuff management screen to manage it.

3. If you have the demo installation, you can add the interview templates in this package (interview/install/sample_templates) by copying them to templates folder. You will need to go to Campsite admin -> templates afterwards to register them.

Create an section "Interviews" using number 80. Use interview/section-interview.tpl as section and article template. Create an new Interview n admin and check the Interviews section in frontend.
